Full visual:
According to the aviation regulations, the flight was carried out according to the rules of the visual flight, which implies that the crew must have visibility during the flight and on the ground.
Weather conditions:
Reports in the AICM mentioned adequate conditions for take-off, and as the aircraft advanced to the border area between DF and the State of Mexico there were low-altitude cloud layers.
Selected Routes:
